FBIS4-47765 "drafr085_cs94022" FBIS-AFR-94-085-S Daily Report 3 May 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA Home Affairs Denies Involvement Home Affairs Denies Involvement MB0305063994 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 0500 GMT 3 May 94 MB0305063994 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network English BFN [Text] The Department of Home Affairs has denied that some of its officials were involved in the alleged unlawful storage of ballot papers. The department said in a statement the ballot papers stored in the Simitas Building in Pretoria had been put there on instructions of an official of the Independent Electoral Commission.
